description: Foodies on the streets of New Orleans can get their delicious Louisiana flavor fix on the go, all thanks to Kenny’s Cajun & Creole Mobile Kitchen. Their delectable selection of fresh seafood, po’ boys, BBQ, salads, wings, and homemade burgers is all made with care and quality, and will surely keep you coming back time again. This Southern grub is perfect for any kind of event, so if you’re looking for the best for your guests, you gotta call on Kenny’s Cajun & Creole Mobile Kitchen.
name: Kenny's Cajun & Creole Mobile Kitchen
